EU Says Barroso Proposals to Be Comprehensive Crisis Response

-- B y   J a m e s   G .   N e u g e r
-- 
2011-10-12T10:27:35Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-12/eu-says-barroso-proposals-to-be-comprehensive-crisis-response.html
European Commission President  Jose
Barroso  will outline a “comprehensive” set of proposals to
deal with the debt crisis later today, the commission said.  Barroso will present the “roadmap for stability” to the
European Parliament at 3 p.m. in Brussels, commission
spokeswoman Pia Ahrenkilde Hansen told reporters in Brussels
today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James G. Neuger at 
 jneuger@bloomberg.net  